{"tid":1628402,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"要選擇最有效既方法","createTime":"2019-10-06T02:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T03:07:11.000Z","uid":62385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"09c5afd77508796ce6c9355d3dd184dea43cd2da","tid":1628402,"uid":62385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:42:04.000Z","msg":"唔係裝唔裝修既問題 係裝修帶黎既觀感問題 外國只會覺得你係嬲得滯就報復<br />\n<br />\n勇和要聽人講 唔好一反對就話帶風向 咁同獨裁政權其實無分別<br />\n<br />\n其實警暴材料已經非常多 但根本唔夠文宣 因為太多太散亂<br />\n<br />\n所以 大家要冷靜 be water 集中制造出政府欺壓人民既印象 等外國一面倒支持我地 <br />\n<br />\n我地要反擊 唔一定係同佢地對打 可以罷買罷食撳錢 直接了當亦唔會令我地失去Victim 既地位 <br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好俾政府成功營造出對立 人民鬥人民既畫面 因為佢地最想咁"},{"pid":"d1da17b7795400649624e2f78312dac3b9d83135","tid":1628402,"uid":62385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:43:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39fb5b31dcd313936c5920ec7ced9daef2dc5c01","tid":1628402,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:43:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反緊急法！反獨裁特首</span><br />\nSignature簽名檔：保衛家園，對抗極權<br />\n「反極權運動」守護香港，深層改革<br />\n<br />\n裝修裝飾要小心，最好貼返張紙！<br />\n威力愈強嘅武器愈需要精確度！<br />\n唔偷野、冇私心、為民除害！<br />\n文宣要人呀，民意唔可以逆轉！<br />\n國際戰線第一次危機！<br />\n<br />\n抗爭轉型及進化建議：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">重要目標：</span></strong>11月24號區議會選舉、香港民主及人權法案<br />\n和平勇武後勤文宣議員：各司其職<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">強調：</span></strong>愛港市民、良知、美國制裁、親北京賣港賊、大話精、傀儡、暴政殘害人民、公平公正選舉、為港人服務<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">防範：</span></strong>掌心雷、利誘淺黃淺藍市民、抹黑<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">流水式示威：</span></strong>警察舉旗咪去另一個地方示威，香港咁多地方可以去，佢想捉你，你咪話走緊囉，太多人行得慢好正常，合情合理合法！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">適當武力/自衛反擊：</span></strong>合情又合理！<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>游擊戰？：</strong></span>對抗黑社會/恐怖分子<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">創意活動：抗爭融入生活</span></strong>唱歌比賽？跑步大叫？商場罷買？摺紙？#Shout4HK#諗到再加<br />\n<br />\n公平、自由、民主、公義、人權<span style=\"color: gold;\">得來不易</span><br />\n漫長的道路上需要<span style=\"color: gold;\">你支持我，我扶持你</span><br />\n有時惘然若失，但我們也要<span style=\"color: gold;\">自信往前邁步</span><br />\n有咩嘢唔想失去，就努力<span style=\"color: gold;\">捍衛</span>同<span style=\"color: gold;\">守護</span><br />\n現在就用自己雙手實踐夢想，<span style=\"color: gold;\">迎接未來</span><br />\n<br />\n短期目標：改善抗爭能力，提升身份認同<br />\n建議：文宣！各有各做，best effort <br />\n中期目標：區議會(94%民主產生)<br />\n建議：關注身邊人，團結一致，各有各做<br />\n長期目標：強化黃色陣營、民主/黃色經濟圈<br />\n建議：抗爭生活化，減少比錢極權陣營<br />\n終極目標：民選議會、民選政府<br />\n建議：國際戰線、傳播思想、滲透內部<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公務員</span></strong>：小隱於野，中隱於市，大隱於朝<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和勇合一</strong></span>：1.合法之下，最大勇武<br />\n                     2. 做任何事，永不被捕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">@謠言係疫症&bull;不傳播&bull;去求診&bull;澄清藥<br />\n@FakeNews係Cancer&bull;不擴散&bull;求事實&bull;割<br />\n@接觸資訊時，腦袋要清醒</span><br />\n<br />\n只要爭取民主團火未熄，還是有機會達成<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">衛城革命，生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡，打倒腐敗</span><br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\n<strong><em>升級技能/能力值</em></strong>：1. 讀書、識法律2.運動、鬥長命3.和勇合一精神4.批判性思考5.精通專業技能<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XMdiioB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXMdiioB.jpg&h=7e10cb33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持；Best effort，你呢？民主尚未成功，同志仍需努力<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfEIhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=012eaac2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n理非可以做的事<a href=\"https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTakeActionWithYou&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfEIhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=574372d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou</a><br />\n良心與無良商戶<a href=\"https://www.wordsofmouth.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wordsofmouth.net%2F&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfEIhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=7971037d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wordsofmouth.net/</a><br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\nVersion 2019.10.06<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">要記住極權如何打壓香港示威：</span></strong><br />\n1.抹黑：利用少部分的暴力衝突而將全部示威者形容為「邪惡」、示威=港獨、新華社、環球時報、人民日報<br />\n2.誤導：警總救護車、雷射槍、9吋尖刀等等<br />\n3.滲透：5毛、陳雲、黃x民、譚香文<br />\n4.假民意/曲解民意：主流民意是......<br />\n5.5毛輿論-分化、負面、fake news、煽動手足做負效益/低效益工作<br />\n6.強迫企業自我審查<br />\n7.出動黑社會、愛國暴徒<br />\n8.扮示威者：(負面的)破壞eg.遊行<br />\n9.嫁禍示威者/黑警：打議員打記者打女仔<br />\n10.扮好人/扮對話：「江山易改本性難移」<br />\n11.警察濫權、濫捕、暴力執法、恐嚇<br />\n12.利用親中人士發表「假」權威言論<br />\n13.用盡手段打壓反對聲音<br />\n14.矮化示威者為甲由、yellow object<br />\n諗到再加</span><br />\nSir, my concern is not whether God is on our side; my greatest concern is to be on God's side, for God is always right."},{"pid":"a25217fe1bf14b9e0ca7b0652be57730a6613aed","tid":1628402,"uid":62385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:43:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10d873696c292b256787f1bba962ff94db14b337","tid":1628402,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:43:38.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2eJKVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2eJKVS.png&h=fd892c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GobPu5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGobPu5a.jpg&h=8c19a255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyYDlCk4w_-I&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfEIhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=dc28b4d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I</a>"},{"pid":"98b34ead89556bab80c065516d7217c95d3d6805","tid":1628402,"uid":